k","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/521289.html?thread=25757257#t25757257","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/521289.html?thread=25757257#t25757257","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_3821796","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://twitter.com/stile99","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":25757257,"talkid":100614,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/521289.html?thread=25757257#t25757257","above":25747529,"upictitle":"Howard Wilson II: pic#126513625","article":"He's been doing this for a LONG time now, he's one of the original victims of the virus.  As I believe Tachyon said one time, his body appears to know what it is doing.<br /><br />Add to that my personal opinion: he doesn't 'actually' get re-infected each time, so he may not even have odds of drawing a Black Queen.  We don't fully understand his wild card ability, it might not work the way an infection does.  In fact, at this point in time (again, this is my personal opinion) it's pretty unlikely that he ever WILL draw a BQ, given what the odds of doing so are.  If he hasn't by now, then he's not going to.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 months ago","ctime":"February 19 2017, 21:06:43 UTC","parent":25747529,"massactions":0,"subject":"Re: How is the Sleeper still alive?","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://twitter.com/stile99","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/twitter-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"stile99","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_3821796","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=78506853&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"stile99","ctime_ts":1487538403,"tracked":0},{"shown":0,"collapsed":1,"uname":"laviniagrace","loaded":0,"p_tracked":0,"comm